  },
  {
   "id": 6341,
   "parent": 6323,
   "author": "Marinda Engelbrecht",
   "avatar": "https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f19140ecf5b531edcab42d7f2d07c2fc5516ea5d729fc89d2f660757c2880626?s=96&d=mm&r=g",
   "date": "2023-12-14T10:30:03",
   "html": "<p>Jy kan met groot sukses vries. Haal uit en laat ontdooi en bak in die oond.</p>"
  },
  {
   "id": 6323,
   "parent": 0,
   "author": "Maritha Holland-Muter",
   "avatar": "https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/910b8d48e405df0ddd9a4f8842e7861f28ac0aff0a46cdb2a6c8f56027009bad?s=96&d=mm&r=g",
   "date": "2023-12-11T21:56:45",
   "html": "<p>Naand Marinda<br>\nKan jy my asb help. Kan ek hierdie bobotie resep van jou nou maak en vries vir ongeveer 2 weke. Hoe hanteer ek dan inden ek kan vries, as ek wil voorsit.<br>\nDankie dat jy met ons deel</p>"
  },
  {
   "id": 4565,
   "parent": 4564,
   "author": "Marinda Engelbrecht",
   "avatar": "https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f19140ecf5b531edcab42d7f2d07c2fc5516ea5d729fc89d2f660757c2880626?s=96&d=mm&r=g",
   "date": "2022-09-28T11:26:32",
   "html": "<p>Middag Susan<br>\nEk druk die melk uit die brood en dan werk dit vir ons.  Jy kan enige tyd nog melk en eier meng.<br>\nLekker eet.</p>"
  },
  {
   "id": 4564,
   "parent": 0,
   "author": "Susan Morton",
   "avatar": "https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/68db636dc5347840e84e003cee0a52ef7767df4592b1649bcfa5d2196840f3bc?s=96&d=mm&r=g",
   "date": "2022-09-28T11:10:34",
   "html": "<p>Hallo Marinda</p>\n<p>Wil net hoor by jou, is die 1 eier en bietjie melk wat oorbly van die brood se geweek, nie te min vir n bolaag nie.  Dit gaan die bobotie skaars bedek!<br>\nGroete<br>\nSusan</p>"
  },
  {
   "id": 3802,
   "parent": 3797,
   "author": "Marinda Engelbrecht",
   "avatar": "https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f19140ecf5b531edcab42d7f2d07c2fc5516ea5d729fc89d2f660757c2880626?s=96&d=mm&r=g",
   "date": "2022-03-18T11:27:46",
   "html": "<p>Ek sal se tenminste 8.  Dit hang af hoe groot eters die gaste is.</p>"
  },
